column4: I'm encoding mp3's with rhythmbox.  in editing my "mp3" profile, what do i change?  it encoded at 48kbps, i want 128kbps
gstreamer pipeline: audio/x-raw-int,rate=44100,channels=2 ! lamemp3enc name=enc target=0 quality=6 ! xingmux ! id3v2mux
